UNITED STATES ex rel. Eric LEIBMAN, Appellant, v. William FLYNN, District Director of Immigration in Charge at Buffalo, New York, Respondent. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. October 29, 1928. No. 101. Dominick & Dominick, of Buffalo, N. Y., for appellant. Richard H. Templeton, U. S. Atty., of Buffalo, N. Y. (Harold E. Orr, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Buffalo, N. Y., of counsel), for respondent.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order (16 F.[2d] 1006) affirmed.
